data.description: Welcome to this inviting 2BR/1BA home, nestled on a lush half-acre for ultimate privacy and outdoor enjoyment. Inside, find a modern kitchen leading to a cozy dining area, and a living room perfect for unwinding. The basement offers potential for a bonus room or extra bedroom. The large backyard, ideal for gardening or leisure, includes RV parking. A detached garage plus workshop adds convenience. With a gas stove and updated bathroom, comfort meets style. Situated on a quiet street near town, it's the ideal blend of country living and accessibility. Ready for new owners to make it their own.
